<DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c9"><BR><BR></P>
</DIV>
<DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c30"><SPAN CLASS="c31">n23.&nbsp; A pre-trial probation in a criminal matter usually leads to a dismissal at the end of the probationary period if the defendant satisfies all the conditions. </SPAN></P>
