<DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c30"><SPAN CLASS="c31">n56.&nbsp; At the time, the Chinese Progressive Association had the reputation of being a &quot;leftist&quot; or &quot;communist&quot; organization within the community. </SPAN></P>
