<DIV CLASS="c5"><P CLASS="c30"><SPAN CLASS="c31">n74.&nbsp; See Lydia Lowe &amp; Doug Brugge, Grassroots Organizing in Boston Chinatown: A Comparison with CDC-Style Organizing, in Acting Civically: From Urban Neighborhoods to Higher Education, 44-71 (Susan A. Ostrander &amp; Kent E. Portney, eds., 2007). </SPAN></P>
